Legacy P2P - # Enable the legacy p2p layer (use-legacy = true)

COMMANDS
AppD Daemon Status - systemctl status celestia-appd
Start Node - sudo systemctl start celestia-bridge && sudo journalctl -u  celestia-bridge.service -f
Open Logs - journalctl -u celestia-appd.service -f
Unjail Validator - celestia-appd tx slashing unjail --from=mycelium --chain-id mamaki
Restart App - # restart service. systemctl restart celestia-appd
